    {
      "id": "l-ann-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 82,
      "y": 693,
      "width": 522,
      "height": 190,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#5c3d00",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "text": "❌  Compute-bound to one host — won't scale\n❌  Lower model quality (7B–13B vs Haiku)\n❌  Can't serve multiple clients at once\n❌  High token cost at the extraction step\n❌  No summarization ≠ more context\n      Just more tokens to the capable model",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "❌  Compute-bound to one host — won't scale\n❌  Lower model quality (7B–13B vs Haiku)\n❌  Can't serve multiple clients at once\n❌  High token cost at the extraction step\n❌  No summarization ≠ more context\n      Just more tokens to the capable model",
