      "text": "✅  Scales horizontally — cloud API, no local compute\n✅  Parallel batch calls (Batch API = 50% cheaper)\n✅  ~90% token reduction at the extraction step\n✅  POC validated — 130 reqs from CareFlow docs\n⚠   Real fix: add 35-word chunk overlap\n      to catch requirements that span chunk boundaries",
